[[File:Glasgow District Council election, 1984.svg|thumb|Map showing results in Glasgow District Council wards.]] '''Elections for the [[Glasgow Council|Glasgow City District Council]]''' took place alongside [[Scottish District local elections, 1984|elections to the councils]] of the other [[Local government areas of Scotland 1973–96|districts]] in Scotland. The result was victory for the [[Scottish Labour Party|Labour]] party, who won 59 of the 66 wards.
